  "notes": "Planted issues: (1) SEC-001 \u2014 the literal \"ArchiveP@ss2024!\" is passed as the Archive Password input on 'Get Pending Invoices' instead of a Credential Manager lookup. (2) REL-003 \u2014 'Wait For Confirmation' in the VBO's Enter Invoice page has an empty <timeout/>. (3) MNT-002 \u2014 data item 'Temp Counter' on the Dispatcher's Main Page is never referenced. Parser conventions this sample exercises: WaitEnd maps to IR kind 'anchor' (timeout continuation point); actions on object \"Work Queues\" are queue operations whose Queue Name literal becomes the IR queueName; the VBO's 'Invoice System URL' data item has exposure=Environment binding it to the release's environment variable. The performer's Get Next Item cycle is guarded by the 'Item Retrieved?' decision \u2014 it must NOT trigger REL-002."
